<dl id="n08125b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n08" href="#n08125b">N08 (VI.B.6)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n08all.htm#n08125b"> 125(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> perpetual</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">The &ldquo;Perpetual Rosary&rdquo; is an organization for ensuring the continuous recitation of the Rosary by day and night among a number of associates who perform their allotted share at stated times. <small> <a name="CECRA" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#CECRA"><cite title="source">&ldquo;Coemgen&rdquo;, &ldquo;Rosary&rdquo; and &ldquo;Albigenses&rdquo;</cite></a> <cite a>Catholic Encyclopaedia</cite></a> (1911) XIII, &lsquo;Rosary&rsquo; 189a</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
